105
00:10:34,830 --> 00:10:36,060
Tidak masalah.

106
00:10:36,629 --> 00:10:39,659
Aku mulai penasaran selangka apa panah itu.

107
00:10:47,210 --> 00:10:49,909
Aku mendengar bahwa Anda sakit, tapi tidak datang

108
00:10:50,239 --> 00:10:52,139
