akan segera menyusulmu.

149
00:13:44,550 --> 00:13:45,619
Kejar mereka.

150
00:13:46,249 --> 00:13:49,519
Jangan biarkan anggota keluarganya bertahan hidup.

151
00:13:50,989 --> 00:13:54,859
