220
00:19:00,169 --> 00:19:02,330
Sisa waktuku tidak banyak.

221
00:19:04,740 --> 00:19:05,969
Ayah paham

222
00:19:07,869 --> 00:19:09,109
maksud ucapanmu.

223
00:19:12,209 --> 00:19:13,949
Astaga.

224
00:19:16,709 --> 00:19:17,820
Tuan!

225
00:19:18,050 --> 00:19:20,550
Jangan pergi ke sana.

